ICCF email 2011} cxd6 $11 {With a dream 4.Nbd2 Bogo-Indian setup for Black.})
10... exd5 11. cxd5 (11. Nd4 dxc4 12. Bxb7 Nxb7 13. Nxf5 Be5 14. Bg5 c6 15. Nd1
d5 16. e4 {Pogosyan,S (2349)-Minasian,A (2492) Yerevan 2017 (1/2-1/2, 43)} Qd7
