(2340) Andorra la Vella 2017 (0-1, 36)} O-O 10. a3 Bxc3+ 11. Bxc3 Na6 12. Qd4
f5 13. h3 Nf6 14. O-O-O Nc5 {, with active play.}) 6... Nf6 7. f3 {Slow but
