some lack of balance in his position.} Bxc3+ {If Black intends to fight for
the initiative, this is the best way to do it.} (5... Qh4 6. Bd3 f5 7. Nf3 {
Without the previous exchange on c3, this is the only way to fight for the
initiative.} Bxc3+ 8. Qxc3 $5 {This surprising move offers White chances for a
strong attack.} (8. Kf1 $5 {This is a typical trick Black has to be aware of.
The king will be a bit uncomfortable, but White hopes that the same will be
